%26quot%3Bblend%20it%26quot%3B%20into%20your%20own%20company%2C%20Immad%20Akhund%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20are%20told%20to%20run%20like%20Airbnb%2C%20go%20full%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounder-mode-manager-dividing-silicon-valley-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efounder%20mode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20follow%20OKRs%20%E2%80%94%20Objective%20and%20Key%20Results.%20But%20Immad%20Akhund%2C%20an%20angel%20investor%20since%202016%2C%20said%20copying%20Silicon%20Valley%20playbooks%20can%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20easy%26quot%3B%20to%20try%20to%20copy%20and%20paste%20a%20Brian%20Chesky%20axiom%20to%20your%20situation%2C%20Akhund%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BIn%20Depth%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BThat%20never%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lessons%20work%20in%20their%20particular%20way%20for%20that%20particular%20situation%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20adapt%20them%20to%20your%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAkhund%20said%20the%20key%20is%20to%20understand%20the%20framework%20and%20context%20that%20made%20it%20successful%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Btry%20to%20blend%20it%26quot%3B%20into%20your%20own%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Akhund%2C%20who%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20banking%20startup%20Mercury%2C%20said%20people%20told%20him%20to%20adopt%20an%20OKR%20framework%20once%20the%20company%20reached%20a%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20size.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20small%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20this%20is%20just%20silly%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20need%20a%20structure%20for%20objectives%2C%20like%20there%20are%20just%20five%20people%20in%20the%20room.%20Let's%20just%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20cautioned%20against%20letting%20metrics%20dictate%20every%20decision.%3