0California%3Cp%3EThomson%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMajor%20US%20alcohol%20producers%20are%20urging%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20cut%20tariffs%20ahead%20of%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20alcohol%20association%20representing%20Beam%20Suntory%20and%20Brown-Forman%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20warned%20that%20the%20tariffs%20could%20result%20in%20a%20%242%20billion%20sales%20loss%20and%2025%2C000%20American%20jobs%20lost.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20holiday%20season%20looms%2C%20US%20liquor%20groups%20are%20begging%20Trump%20to%20kill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-what-to-invest-trump-tariffs-tax-bill-playbook-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20say%20could%20ruin%20their%20most%20lucrative%20stretch%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%2057%20associations%20and%20guilds%20called%20the%20Toasts%20not%20Tariffs%20Coalition%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Wednesday%20letter%20to%20the%20White%20House%20that%20tariffs%20could%20result%20in%20a%20%242%20billion%20sales%20loss%20in%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reiterate%20our%20urgent%20request%20that%20the%20U.S.%20and%20EU%20come%20to%20an%20agreement%20to%20secure%20fair%20and%20reciprocal%20trade%20on%20spirits%20and%20wine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20approach%20the%20critical%20holiday%20season%2C%20a%20period%20that%20is%20essential%20to%20the%20success%20of%20our%20industries%2C%20we%20implore%20you%20to%20secure%20this%20important%20deal%20for%20the%20U.S.%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20comes%20as%20Trump's%20new%20tariffs%20went%20into%20effect%20at%20midnight%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20being%20slammed%20with%20a%2015%25%20tariff%20rate%20on%20most%20goods.%20However%2C%20t