0can%20to%20raise%20cash%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20committed%20to%20building%20a%20streaming%20business%2C%20you%20have%20to%20put%20as%20much%20firepower%20behind%20them%20as%20you%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20necessarily%20an%20all-or-nothing%20game%2C%20as%20he%20sees%20it.%20%26quot%3BThey'll%20want%20to%20keep%20CBS%20to%20keep%20their%20leverage%20with%20the%20distribution%20world%2C%20and%20with%20the%20NFL%2C%20the%20consumer%20value%20the%20network%20brings%20is%20really%20important.%26quot%3B%20Others%2C%20like%20BET%20and%20Showtime%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that%20Paramount%20tried%20to%20sell%20before%20%E2%80%94%20could%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226de2f8ee-c281-462c-98d4-5867c416f102%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20Trump%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnxieties%20have%20been%20running%20high%20for%20some%20people%20in%20and%20outside%20CBS's%20news%20division%2C%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20repeatedly%20targeting%20the%20news%20media.%20Paramount%20agreed%20to%20a%20%2416%20million%20settlement%20over%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20Trump%20over%20routine%20editing%20of%20a%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20segment%20that%20many%20legal%20experts%20said%20was%20meritless%20%E2%80%94%20a%20settlement%20that%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-trump-settlement-media-politics-reactions-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elambasted%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20journalism%20and%20political%20circles%20as%20a%20concession%20to%20get%20the%20Skydance%20deal%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20has%20disputed%20this%2C%20saying%20the%20settlement%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20separate%20from%2C%20and%20unrelated%20to%2C%20the%20Skydance%20transaction.%26quot%3B%20Skydance%20went%20on%20to%20agree%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fcc-approves-skydance-paramount-merger-content-conditions-diversity-2025-7%5C%22%20targe