%20the%20right%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20producer%20Rome%20Hartman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolitics%20aside%2C%20it's%20also%20not%20hard%20to%20imagine%20Paramount%20using%20CBS%20News%20to%20help%20get%20to%20its%20%242%20billion%20in%20cost%20cuts%2C%20given%20it's%20already%20trailing%20the%20other%20news%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb42ead6-81c1-4139-98d2-fb41bc54e187%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20games%20jump-start%20Paramount%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESkydance%20has%20two%20video%20game%20studios%2C%20and%20Ellison%20sees%20games%20as%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20Skydance%20can%20kick-start%20Paramount's%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20games%20are%20a%20conundrum%20for%20Hollywood%20companies%3B%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuicide-squad-video-game-failed-cost-warner-brothers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpensive%20and%20risky%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20ignoring%20them%20means%20missing%20a%20big%20opportunity%20to%20extend%20their%20IP%20to%20a%20hugely%20popular%20pastime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20and%20Disney%20have%20taken%20stabs%20at%20games%20with%20mixed%20success%2C%20and%20Netflix%20is%20building%20out%20its%20games%2C%20but%20has%20yet%20to%20show%20meaningful%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Ellison%20could%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20leverage%20Paramount's%20well%20known%20IP%20into%20games%20success%2C%20he'd%20accomplish%20something%20few%20others%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bca1867-a559-4324-b757-62a6b9812f45%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20endgame%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Skydance%20still%20isn't%20considered%20big%20enough%20to%20hold%20its%20own%20among%20bigger%20media%20and%20tech%20giants%2C%20and%20industry%20observers%20expect%20more%20consolidation%20will%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20said%20Paramount%20Skydance%20could%20be%20a%20good%20pairing%20with%20Warner%2C%20with%20HBO%20Max's%20prestige%