%20at%20the%20soldier's%20place%20of%20work.%20It%20did%20involve%20his%20coworkers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Five%20soldiers%20walk%20in%20a%20line%20on%20pavement%20with%20grass%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20a%20building%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20sky%20is%20blue%20with%20some%20clouds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893bce0f748d8c055f70597%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELubas%20said%20Army%20officials%20were%20determining%20how%20the%20suspect%20got%20his%20handgun%20on%20base.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Pfc.%20Jude%20Vogel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20in%20the%20area%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20and%20without%20hesitation%20tackled%26quot%3B%20the%20shooting%20suspect%2C%20subduing%20him%20before%20law%20enforcement%20took%20him%20into%20custody%2C%20Lubas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20press%20conference%2C%20Lubas%20said%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20any%20behavioral%20issues%20involving%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20and%20confirmed%20that%20they%20did%20not%20use%20a%20military%20weapon.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20it%20was%20a%20personal%20handgun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Lubas%20said%20it%20was%20unclear%20how%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20got%20the%20handgun%20on%20base.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadford%2C%20Lubas%20said%2C%20had%20been%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20driving%20under%20the%20influence%20in%20May.%20His%20chain%20of%20command%20was%20unaware%20of%20these%20charges%20prior%20to%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20violent%20incidents%20at%20US%20military%20bases%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20some%20described%20by%20law%20enforcement%20and%20military%20officials%20as%20workplace%20shootings%20and%20others%20as%20acts%20of%20terrorism.%C2%A0%3C%2