%20capabilities%20of%20its%20allies%20and%20partners.%20In%20April%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-secretary-floored-by-ally-south-koreas-shipbuilding-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethen-Navy%20Secretary%20Carlos%20Del%20Toro%20visited%20a%20South%20Korean%20shipyard%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bfloored%20at%20the%20level%20of%20digitization%20and%20real-time%20monitoring%20of%20shipbuilding%20progress%2C%20with%20readily%20available%20information%20down%20to%20individual%20pieces%20of%20stock%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20trip%2C%20Del%20Toro%20encouraged%20South%20Korean%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20commercial%20and%20naval%20shipbuilding%20facilities%20in%20the%20US%2C%20as%20many%20were%20%26quot%3Blargely%20intact%20and%20dormant%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bripe%20for%20redevelopment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20Navy%20secretary%2C%20John%20Phelan%2C%20visited%20both%20Hanwha%20Ocean%20Shipbuilding%20and%20HD%20Hyundai%20Heavy%20Industries%20in%20April%20and%20emphasized%20the%20value%20of%20South%20Korean%20yards%20in%20helping%20the%20US%20Navy%20maintain%20readiness%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20a%20priority%20theater%20where%20competition%20with%20China%2C%20a%20shipbuilding%20juggernaut%20with%20a%20substantial%20fleet%2C%20is%20a%20key%20focus%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeveraging%20the%20expertise%20of%20these%20highly%20capable%20shipyards%20enables%20timely%20maintenance%20and%20repairs%20for%20our%20vessels%20to%20operate%20at%20peak%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Phelan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20level%20of%20large-scale%20repair%20and%20maintenance%20capability%20strengthens%20our%20combat%20readiness%2C%20sustains%20forward%20deployed%20operational%20presence%2C%20and%20reinforces%20regional%20stability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20v