2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-ng-vibe-coding-unfortunate-term-exhausting-job-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20start%20to%20realize%2C%20wow%2C%20these%20things%20could%20move%20way%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Rowan%20Trollope%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Redis%2C%20a%20software%20company%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20immediately%20approved%20the%20use%20of%20all%20AI-assisted%20coding%20tools.%20Then%20the%20company%20launched%20a%20weeklong%20hackathon%20that%20challenged%20teams%20of%20employees%20to%20%26quot%3Buse%20all%20the%20latest%20and%20greatest%20AI%20technologies%20to%20do%20something%20cool%2C%26quot%3B%20Trollope%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20have%20found%2C%20however%2C%20that%20despite%20the%20excitement%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20millions%20in%20funding%20pouring%20into%20vibe%20coding%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20technology%20is%20still%20limited.%20So%2C%20many%20CEOs%20are%20developing%20new%20policies%20and%20tools%20to%20maximize%20the%20benefits%20of%20vibe%20coding%20while%20mitigating%20the%20pitfalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%20coding%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20when%20developers%20(or%20anyone%2C%20really)%20prompt%20AI%20to%20generate%20code.%20In%20a%20survey%20of%20hundreds%20of%20engineers%20in%20May%2C%20Jellyfish%2C%20a%20software%20intelligence%20platform%2C%20found%20that%2090%25%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethem%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-tools-popular-github-gemini-code-assist-cursor-q-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintegrated%20AI%20into%20their%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20up%20from%2061%25%20just%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%20coding%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-tech-firms-hire-engineers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20marketable%20skill%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Companies%20from%20Visa%20to%20Reddit%20to%20DoorDash%20are%20posting%20jobs%20that%20require%20vibe%20coding%20experience%20or%20familiarity%20with%20AI%20coding%20tools.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-candidates-use-ai-coding-interviews-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20now%20allows%20job%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20use%20an%20AI%20assistant%20in%20their%20coding%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-competition-big-tech-meta-talent-windsurf-amazon-movie-deepmind-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoined%20by%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20cofounder%20Andrej%20Karpathy%20in%20February.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20coding%20I%20call%20'vibe%20coding%2C'%20where%20you%20fully%20give%20in%20to%20the%20vibes%2C%20embrace%20exponentials%2C%20and%20forget%20that%20the%20code%20even%20exists%2C%26quot%3B%20Karpathy%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20see%20stuff%2C%20say%20stuff%2C%20run%20stuff%2C%20and%20copy-paste%20stuff%2C%20and%20it%20mostly%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELimits%20to%20the%20technology%20remain%2C%20however.%20Though%20vibe%20coding%20promises%20quick%20productivity%20gains%C2%A0and%20allows%20people%20with%20little%20coding%20experience%20to%20create%20software%2C%C2%A0tech%20executives%20say%20AI%20is%20still%20prone%20to%20mistakes%2C%20often%20writes%20unnecessarily%20long%20code%2C%20or%20lacks%20the%20proper%20architecture.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESo%20Trollope%20and%20other%20tech%20CEOs%20have%20had%20to%20introduce%20parameters%20for%20its%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrollope%20said%20vibe%20coding%20is%20best%20for%20building%20proof%20of%20concepts%2C%20writing%20tests%2C%20and%20validating%20existing%20code%2C%20but%20not%20necessarily%20developing%20any%20of%20the%20company's%20core%20software.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20not%20in%20a%20place%20yet%20where%20we%20would%20trust%20it%20with%20our%20core%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20still%20limited%2C%20this%20new%2C%20more%20freewheeling%20approach%20has%20gained%20momentum%20in%20part%20thanks%20to%20the%20money%20flowing%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-vc-technical-founders-skills-investors-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibe%20coding%20platforms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20month%2C%20Anysphere%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Cursor%2C%20an%20AI-assisted%20code%20editor%2C%20announced%20a%20%24900%20million%20Series%20C%20fundraise%20at%20a%20%249.9%20billion%20valuation.%20Wix%2C%20a%20web-development%20platform%2C%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20acquired%20the%20vibe%20coding%20platform%20Base44%20for%20%2480%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplit%2C%20a%20code%20editor%2C%20saw%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erevenue%20grow%20fivefold%20in%20September%20after%20it%20released%20Agent%2C%20a%20coding%20assistant%20that%20works%20with%20natural%20language%20prompts.%20By%20June%2C%20the%20company%20landed%20a%20new%20%24250%20million%20funding%20round%20that%20brought%20its%20valuation%20to%20%243%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%20Swedish%20vibe%20coding%20startup%20Lovable%2C%20one%20of%20Europe's%20fastest-growing%20startups%2C%20raised%20%24200%20million%20in%20Series%20A%20funding%20in%20July%20at%20a%20%241.8%20billion%20valuation%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20frenzy%20pushed%20Airtable%2C%20a%20database%20development%20platform%2C%20to%20relaunch%20last%20month%20as%20a%20fully%20AI-native%20platform.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20overhaul%2C%20the%20company%20created%20an%20app-building%20assistant%20called%20Omni%20for%20vibe%20coders.%20It%20allows%20developers%20to%20%26quot%3Bconversationally%20vibe%20generate%20the%20app%20they%20want%2C%20but%20understand%20what's%20been%20generated%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20the%20data%20and%20logic%20layer%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Airtable%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20announcing%20the%20overhaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20still%20a%20question%20of%3A%20Is%20that%20an%20AI%20tourist%20attraction%3F%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20durable%3F%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20high%20churn%3F%26quot%3B%20Airtable%20CEO%20Howie%20Liu%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20%26quot%3Ball%20these%20people%20are%20coming%20in%20and%20pulling%20out%20their%20credit%20cards%20to%20try%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%20For%20Airtable%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20fully%20reinventing%20ourselves%20is%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20guaranteed%20path%20to%20obsolescence%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20launch%20of%20Omni%2C%20Liu%20also%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20correct%20some%20of%20the%20problems%20that%20come%20with%20vibe%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20vibe%20coding%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20not%20really%20inspecting%20the%20code%2C%20you're%20not%20really%20thinking%20about%20the%20technical%20architecture%2C%20you're%20just%20telling%20it%20what%20you%20want%20it%20to%20build%20and%20kind%20of%20like%20clicking%20the%20'I'm%20feeling%20lucky%20button%2C'%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20magical%20thing%20is%20like%20the%20AI%20has%20gotten%20good%20enough%20that%20it%20seemingly%20just%20works%20some%20of%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%20But%20even%20apps%20that%20%26quot%3Bseemingly%20work%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftea-app-data-breach-cybersecurity-ai-vibe-coding-safety-experts-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20riddled%20with%20errors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20security%20vulnerabilities%20at%20their%20deeper%2C%20infrastructure%20layers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20perfect%20world%2C%20developers%20could%20leverage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagi-predictions-sam-altman-dario-amodei-geoffrey-hinton-demis-hassabis-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3