he%20space.%20Dizzying%20demand%20for%20data%20centers%20has%20created%20an%20equally%20enormous%20need%20for%20power.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Finsights%2Farticles%2Fai-to-drive-165-increase-in-data-center-power-demand-by-2030%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredicts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20data%20center%20power%20demand%20will%20increase%20165%25%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20sparked%20a%20search%20for%20alternative%20power%20sources%20to%20support%20the%20continued%20growth%20of%20data%20centers%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20easy%20and%20fast%20to%20reactivate%20nuclear%20reactors%20to%20meet%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20clean%20energy%20from%20data%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alexander%20Lis%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Social%20Discovery%20Ventures.%20%26quot%3BOther%20energy%20sources%20were%20either%20less%20clean%2C%20like%20coal%2C%20or%20longer%20to%20build%2C%20like%20wind%20or%20solar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELis%20added%20that%20his%20firm%20considers%20this%20demand%20to%20be%20sustainable%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bmany%20big%20tech%20companies%20have%20already%20announced%20their%20plans%20to%20use%20nuclear%20energy%20for%20their%20data%20centers.%26quot%3B%20Last%20September%2C%20Constellation%20Energy%20said%20it%20would%20reopen%20Three%20Mile%20Island%2C%20with%20Microsoft%20set%20to%20purchase%20the%20power%20power%20generated%20by%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Schiffer%2C%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20The%20Patriarch%20Organization%20and%20a%20nuclear%20energy%20investor%2C%20echoed%20this%20sentiment%2C%20highlighting%20the%20role%20that%20it%20may%20play%20in%20helping%20the%20US%20achieve%20AI%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20%5Bis%5D%20far%20more%20equipped%20right%20now%20from%20an%20energy%20platform%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%20%26quot%3BNuclear%20is%20a%20critical%20piece%20to%20ensure%20we're%20staying%20at