miled%2C%20promising%20to%20return%20it%20on%20his%20next%20trip.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20simple%20act%20%E2%80%94%20but%20one%20that%20ties%20strangers%20together%20through%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20story%20you%20can%20add%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20an%20age%20of%20screens%20and%20scrolling%2C%20where%20the%20habit%20of%20reading%20feels%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20slipping%20away.%20For%20children%2C%20especially%2C%20imagination%20often%20comes%20second%20to%20instant%20entertainment.%20The%20Flybrary%20gently%20pushes%20back%20against%20that%20trend.%20It%20says%20books%20still%20matter%3B%20that%20stories%20still%20have%20the%20power%20to%20pause%20us%2C%20comfort%20us%2C%20and%20make%20the%20world%20feel%20less%20lonely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20something%20special%20about%20holding%20a%20book%20that%20has%20passed%20through%20other%20hands%20%E2%80%94%20hands%20that%20turned%20these%20very%20pages%20on%20other%20journeys%2C%20in%20other%20moments.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20the%20Flybrary%20more%20than%20just%20a%20shelf.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20chain%20of%20generosity%2C%20stitched%20together%20by%20people%20who%20believe%20in%20sharing%20something%20as%20simple%20and%20beautiful%20as%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20next%20time%20you%20pack%20for%20a%20flight%2C%20slip%20in%20an%20extra%20one.%20Leave%20it%20on%20the%20shelf%20before%20you%20board.%20Somewhere%2C%20someone%20will%20find%20it%20exactly%20when%20they%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754401488000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1754400933.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D481918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20Bhubaneswar%20Airport%2C%20two%20shelves%20of%20books%20are%20making%20travel%20softer%20and%20kinder.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Flybrary%20runs%20on%20trust%20and%20love%20for