0with%20GFL%20in%202016%20after%20hearing%20about%20the%20company%20from%20a%20fellow%20poultry%20farmer.%20With%20the%20biggest%20farm%20capacity%20among%20women%20in%20CBF%20South%2C%20Bhagyama%E2%80%99s%20business%20has%20enabled%20her%20to%20repay%20a%20family%20loan%2C%20support%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20wedding%2C%20contribute%20to%20her%20grandchildren%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20and%20help%20build%20a%20new%20home.%20Her%20strong%20relationship%20with%20GFL%E2%80%99s%20field%20staff%20is%20rooted%20in%20mutual%20trust%20and%20respect%2C%20a%20key%20ingredient%20in%20her%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20women%20carved%20their%20own%20paths%20in%20agriculture%20and%20field%20work%2C%20GFL%20realised%20there%20was%20potential%20to%20amplify%20such%20impact%20through%20structured%20support.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20WINGS%20%E2%80%94%20a%20focused%20effort%20to%20bring%20more%20women%20into%20frontline%20sales%2C%20a%20space%20historically%20dominated%20by%20men.%20Because%20when%20women%20are%20trusted%20with%20opportunity%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20deliver%20results.%20They%20transform%20everything%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenging%20gender%20norms%20in%20frontline%20sales%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20be%20honest%2C%20frontline%20sales%20isn%E2%80%99t%20for%20the%20faint%20of%20heart.%20It%20comes%20with%20targets%2C%20travel%2C%20pressure%2C%20people%20management%2C%20and%20day-to-day%20unpredictability.%20It%20demands%20presence%20in%20the%20market%2C%20relationship%20building%2C%20and%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20consumer%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20this%20space%20was%20seen%20as%20too%20demanding%20for%20women.%20But%20GFL%20took%20a%20different%20view%3A%20with%20the%20right%20training%20and%20mentorship%2C%20women%20could%20not%20only%20succeed%20in%20sales%2C%20they%20could%20transform%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20behind%20