8Entertainment%20Kothi%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20called%20locally%2C%20%3Cem%3EChaman%20Wali%20Kothi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20After%201959%2C%20due%20to%20some%20family%20disputes%2C%20%3Cem%3EAsafi%20Mahal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20originally%20included%20a%20few%20other%20%3Cem%3Ekothis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(homes)%2C%20was%20divided%2C%20and%20my%20father%20and%20his%20eldest%20brother%20inherited%20%3Cem%3EChaman%20Wali%20Kothi%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Taqi%20would%20often%20watch%20film%20crews%20set%20up%20and%20shoot%20at%20his%20place.%20And%20when%20he%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20past%20that%20later%20defined%20his%20present%2C%20it%20is%20what%20we%20see%20today%20%E2%80%94%20a%20movement%20started%20by%20one%2C%20but%20loved%20by%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDigging%20into%20a%20family%20archive%2C%20finding%20his%20individuality%20and%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20soul%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20grade%2011%2C%20and%20one%20day%2C%20in%20my%20family%20archives%2C%20I%20found%20photographs%20of%20Rekha%20ji%2C%20Farooq%20Shaikh%20ji%2C%20and%20the%20cast%20of%20%3Cem%3EUmrao%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20That%20discovery%20deeply%20intrigued%20me.%20Later%2C%20watching%20the%20film%20and%20recognising%20scenes%20shot%20inside%20my%20own%20home%20sparked%20a%20curiosity%20in%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20us%20that%20over%20the%20years%2C%20scenes%20from%20films%20and%20shows%20like%20%3Cem%3EMirzapur%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20also%20shot%20in%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archives%20of%20Umrao%20Jaan's%20cast%20featuring%20Rekha%20Ji%20(L)%20Dilip%20Kumar%20Ji%20attend