%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3ETaqi%20Abbas%2C%2028%2C%20founder%20of%20Lucknow%20Uncovered%2C%20brings%20to%20light%20overlooked%20stories%20of%20people%20and%20places%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20good%204K%20M4%20mirrorless%20camera%20costs%20around%20Rs%201.5%20to%202.5%20lakh%2C%20and%20then%20there%20are%20lenses%2C%20a%20gimbal%2C%20and%20basic%20lights.%20All%20of%20this%20together%20can%20cost%20around%20Rs%205.5%20to%207.5%20lakh.%20But%20this%20equipment%20can%20easily%20be%20rented%20for%20around%20Rs%207%2C000%20a%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20also%20recurring%20costs.%20A%20lot%20of%20content%20creators%20say%20they%20have%20a%20production%20house%2C%20but%20they%20mostly%20shoot%20and%20edit%20by%20themselves.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20hire%20people%2C%20salaries%20must%20be%20paid%20on%20time.%20Also%2C%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20software%20for%20post-production%20can%20significantly%20increase%20output%20quality%2C%20adding%20around%20one%20lakh%20rupees%20to%20the%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taqi%20explains%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289179%2Fayush-wadhwa-owled-media-video-startup-ankur-warikoo-linkedin-viral%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudding%20creators.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20all%20of%20this%20is%20doable%20with%20some%20smart%20work%20and%20savings%20%E2%80%94%20because%20he%2C%20too%2C%20started%20with%20nothing%2C%20and%20now%20works%20with%20gear%20worth%20Rs%2025%E2%80%9330%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELucknow%20beyond%20the%20obvious%20kebabs%2C%20Chikankari%2C%20or%20Imambara%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20often%20see%20on%20social%20media%20about%20Lucknow%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%3C%2Fem%3E%20trails%20in%20%3Cem%3EChowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20sunset%20shots%20at%20the%20