ld%20a%20swimming%20pool%20using%20nothing%20but%20natural%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20no%20cement%2C%20no%20chemicals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479099%2Fca-chemical-free-swimming-pools-biosphere-coimbatore%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Escape%20City%20Life%20in%20This%20Fairytale%20Mud%20Home%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Built%20by%2090%20People%20From%2018%20Countries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%20courtesy%3A%20Atik%20Bheda%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20feature%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20replica%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask%20Raghav%20Kumar%20(30)%2C%20one%20half%20of%20the%20brother%20duo%20that%20has%20conceptualised%20a%20600-sq%20ft%20beauty%20in%20the%20heartland%20of%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand.%20As%20fans%20of%20the%20seven-part%20fantasy%20series%20%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%20will%20immediately%20guess%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20eight-foot-tall%20giant%20Rubeus%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20cabin%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20The%20Forbidden%20Forest%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20wood%20filled%20with%20wizarding%20creatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosy%20fires%2C%20larger-than-life%20teacups%2C%20and%20a%20drooling%20boarhound%20Fang%20filled%20most%20evenings%20that%20Harry%20and%20his%20friends%20spent%20at%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s.%20I%20often%20found%20myself%20craving%20to%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wish%20might%20just%20have%20been%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20and%20Ansh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%E2%80%99%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20abode.%20Creating%20the%2015-ft%20doppelganger%20homestay%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20goal